name: Oval Cannister HD Knob
description: The Oval Cannister has a bejeweled touch with its delicate knob. Handmade from shagreen, pen shell, snakeskin, bronze-patina brass, and wood veneer interior. Wipe clean with a soft dry cloth. Made in Philippines. The design reflects a quirky mix of inlay patterns inspired by galactic constellations, adding a whimsical element to Kifu's collection.
